ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

ElementDescription: Sex of subject at birth
Notes: M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: How well do the things you do work to make the PROBLEMS better?
Notes: 1=Not at all; 2= A little; 3= Somewhat; 4= very well

ElementDescription: How well do the things you do work to make you FEEL better?
Notes: 1=Not at all; 2= A little; 3= Somewhat; 4= very well

ElementDescription: How satisfied are you with how you cope with stress?
Notes: 1=Not at all; 2= A little; 3= Somewhat; 4= very satisfied

ElementDescription: Compared to other people how well do you handle stress?
Notes: 1=Not at all; 2= A little; 3= Somewhat; 4= very well

ElementDescription: In the coming months, how good of a job do you think you WILL DO coping with stress and problems that come up?
Notes: 1=Not at all; 2= A little; 3= Somewhat; 4= very well

ElementDescription: In the coming months, how good do you think you WILL BE at handling your feelings when problems come up?
Notes: 1=Not at all; 2= A little; 3= Somewhat; 4= very well

ElementDescription: Total All Coping Efficacy Scale Items
When I am confronted with a problem, I can usually find several solutions
Notes: 0 = Not at all true; 1 = Hardly true; 2 = Moderately true; 3 = Exactly true; 999 = Missing

ElementDescription: If I am in trouble, I can usually think of a solution
Notes: 0 = Not at all true; 1 = Hardly true; 2 = Moderately true; 3 = Exactly true; 999 = Missing

ElementDescription: I can usually handle whatever comes my way
Notes: 0 = Not at all true; 1 = Hardly true; 2 = Moderately true; 3 = Exactly true; 999 = Missing

ElementDescription: I can always manage to solve difficult problems if I try hard enough
Notes: 0 = Not at all true; 1 = Hardly true; 2 = Moderately true; 3 = Exactly true; 999 = Missing

ElementDescription: If someone opposes me, I can find the means and ways to get what I want
Notes: 0 = Not at all true; 1 = Hardly true; 2 = Moderately true; 3 = Exactly true; 999 = Missing

ElementDescription: It is easy for me to stick to my aims and accomplish my goals
Notes: 0 = Not at all true; 1 = Hardly true; 2 = Moderately true; 3 = Exactly true; 999 = Missing

ElementDescription: I am confident that I could deal efficiently with unexpected events
Notes: 0 = Not at all true; 1 = Hardly true; 2 = Moderately true; 3 = Exactly true; 999 = Missing

ElementDescription: Thanks to my resourcefulness, I know how to handle unforeseen situations
Notes: 0 = Not at all true; 1 = Hardly true; 2 = Moderately true; 3 = Exactly true; 999 = Missing

ElementDescription: I can solve most problems if I invest the necessary effort
Notes: 0 = Not at all true; 1 = Hardly true; 2 = Moderately true; 3 = Exactly true; 999 = Missing

ElementDescription: I can remain calm when facing difficulties because I can rely on my coping abilities
Notes: 0 = Not at all true; 1 = Hardly true; 2 = Moderately true; 3 = Exactly true; 999 = Missing
